title: 50 Cent interview and More
itunes:title: 50 Cent interview and More
description:
Today on the show we had the King of all pettiness 50 cent! He spoke about his show Power, new projects, and finessing his way out of cancelled culture. Moreover, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the day" to a Connecticut woman for getting pulled over twice in one day for a DUI. Also, we opened up the phone lines to see how often our listeners use filters for pictures.
